<subSubSection pageId="44" pageNumber="45" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="44.[151,1436,151,213]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,151,176]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Distribution.</emphasis>
A rare and little known species so far only known from the Rhone valley near Lyon, and the Mediterranean coast, southern 
<collectingCountry box="[496,572,189,212]" name="France" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">France</collectingCountry>
and a single specimen from central 
<collectingCountry box="[978,1045,188,213]" name="Spain" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Spain</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
